dct_title_s: Zaire city map 1:12,500. Bukavu. Series Z901
dct_description_sm: North Decimal Degree -2.451111. South Decimal Degree -2.532500. East Decimal Degree 28.913889. West Decimal Degree 28.824167. Alternate title: Bukavu. Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 10m. Contour interval and spot heights. Horizontal datum World Geodetic System (WGS) 1984. Vertical datum mean sea level. Guide to numbered features on the map "Standard map series designation: Series Z901.".
dct_publisher_sm: Bethesda, MD : United States. Defense Mapping Agency. Hydrographic/Topographic Center, 1994.
